if you want to change the rasolution do this: right click on the shortcut on the deskto then propertie then in the TARGEt field add RESOLUTION=1024x768x32 and click apply. Leave space between .exe" and RESOLUTION=1024x768x32.
it looks like this "F:\FIFA 08\FIFA08 Demo.exe" RESOLUTION=1024x768x32 (in my case)
Sorry for my poor english. Enjoy!!!!!
